Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.74,0:00:04.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So the 'rin' in Hino Rintaro is just\Nthe 'rin' in ethics violation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.84,0:00:09.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to be sued for this photo,\Nwanna buy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.32,0:00:11.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I refuse, please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:00:12.27,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Calm down a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.12,0:00:15.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then for this picture, how much\Nare you asking to sell it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.88,0:00:18.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The doctor over here gets what I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.80,0:00:22.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,How about 50 million?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:24.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You said 50 million..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:27.27,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You wanna pay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.08,0:00:30.27,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Rintaro, the medical ethics transgressor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.27,0:00:34.79,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.48,0:00:37.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah!\N{\3c&H573235&}What..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.76,0:00:39.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:42.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,er...you..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:45.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ki..Kiku..\N{\3c&H573235&}Kikuchiyo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:48.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah Kikuchiyo-san Kikuchiyo-san!\NI knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.96,0:00:52.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No.. you haven't change!\N{\3c&H573235&}What? Are you an old customer?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:55.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.. I was brought by my senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:00:58.27,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And though I only met you twice,\NI remember you served me sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.88,0:01:03.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I can see you haven't change..still beautiful.\N{\3c&H573235&}Stop it, what are you saying..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.48,0:01:07.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I mean,\Nyou give off this impressive aura,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.92,0:01:11.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,is it called a mature sex appeal?\N{\3c&H573235&}I just..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:13.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Nah..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:17.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Something that when stare at, you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:18.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,can't help but get sucked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.00,0:01:22.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's too pretentious!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.74,0:01:25.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.00,0:01:30.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Isn't the detective coming any time now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:33.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's right, the police is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:37.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,A detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.56,0:01:40.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You see, he's a psychiatrist, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.52,0:01:42.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Occasionally, a patient like that comes here,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.96,0:01:45.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,with a dangerous entangled incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.84,0:01:48.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If that's the case...I'll just be a bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:50.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino-rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:52.77,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Next, I'll give you a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:56.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Keep the 50 million prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:01:57.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:01.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.26,0:02:04.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:08.77,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Senpai, \Nthank you for using your wit quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.68,0:02:13.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So that person is the mother\Nwho is causing problems to the geisha?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:14.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.64,0:02:20.77,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You know, a face like that..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:25.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,is from someone who has been extorting\Nand deceiving people many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.24,0:02:33.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You want to apologize to Yumeno?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.08,0:02:38.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The truth is that the other day\NI had a party with my colleagues
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.48,0:02:40.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and I invited her there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:42.27,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So that was the case.\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.40,0:02:44.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And even though she told me she's shy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:48.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid that my forced invitation,\Nwas an inconvenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.32,0:02:51.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Actually, there's no such a shy girl here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:53.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,, at the parlor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.72,0:02:55.85,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I want to apologize to her,\Nabout that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:03:00.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-chan, wait.\NNow, they are discussing an important matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:02.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, the Dir. Ennoji will call you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:03.77,Default 1,,0,0,0,,O-kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:09.27,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The one who should be apologizing is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.24,0:03:14.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because I didn't notice that child was sick\Nuntil you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:19.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumechiyo-san,\Neven living together,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:22.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,there are many times when it passes unnoticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:25.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I think that it's because the contact with her mother
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:27.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,increased, her symptoms appeared stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:31.77,Default 1,,0,0,0,,with her mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:42.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san, good evening.\N{\3c&H573235&}Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:51.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The acquisition negotiations of\NSoumei medical corporation,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:53.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,have almost reach to an agreement on the amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:57.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Wow .. that's a huge hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.36,0:04:01.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,How much?\N{\3c&H573235&}An unprecedented amount of 60 billion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:02.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,60 billion!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:05.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's pretty big, for a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:08.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Considering it's with the land,\Nit's cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:09.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:13.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, regarding the matter of subsidies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah.. about that..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:18.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I can ask something first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.08,0:04:20.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,what would be that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:22.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to treat one patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:26.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,A patient?\N{\3c&H573235&}Yeah, I think it's brain tumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:29.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well, that's Hasumi-kun's specialized field.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:32.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes, of what kind is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:36.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, I don't know much more than the illness, but
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:39.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,do you know someone called Kusunoki Shozo?\NThe minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.24,0:04:42.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's his only son.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:44.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The fact is that the minister Kusunoki is the authority
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:47.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,for the approval of the subsidiary aid.\N{\3c&H573235&}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:51.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That means, whether we can\Nreceive the 5 billion subsidy or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:54.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,depends on Prof. Hasumi's hands, so to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.84,0:04:58.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're really straightforward.\NBut you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:05:00.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah..that was a slip of the tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:01.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is it okay? Hasumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:07.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This.. depends on my part.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:10.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Don't say such negative words here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:15.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hasumi,\Ndon't you want to do something to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:20.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you succeed, everyone here will be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:22.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:25.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hasumi-kun is one of the best brain surgeons in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:27.77,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm relying on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:30.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:32.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, let's toast, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:35.27,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Just before that..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.72,0:05:39.35,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:48.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Press Secretary Ike,\Nnice to meet you, my name is Araki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:54.26,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Here
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:06:00.16,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Hasumi, did you forget my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:03.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:06.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Araki-kun and Hasumi-kun\Nare our contemporaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:09.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since he is a psychiatrist,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:11.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of letting him in\Nthe place of Hino-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.32,0:06:13.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:17.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If so, what is going to happen\Nto Hino-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:19.82,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He's brilliant, but
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:22.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,he doesn't listen to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:24.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He's under consideration from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:29.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:31.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:33.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.00,0:06:39.33,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Good evening, I'm Yumeno.\N{\3c&H573235&}Yumeno-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:43.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ike-chan, I wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:48.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Me too.\N{\3c&H573235&}Hey, what were you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.16,0:06:50.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, just another talk fun for adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.92,0:06:52.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, today\Nlet's drink a good sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:54.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Get it ready.\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:56.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, how are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:58.79,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:01.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah..we met a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:19.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino\NWhat does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:21.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,, Is it true that Araki is returning to psychiatry?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:22.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What are you..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:24.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!\N{\3c&H573235&}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:29.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I just felt a little dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.64,0:07:33.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You haven't been informed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:35.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wasn't inform of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:38.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That bastard, what is he thinking.\N{\3c&H573235&}Dr. Hasumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:41.27,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:44.27,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Can you see my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:48.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Don't ask stupid things.\N{\3c&H573235&}You need to have an eyesight test.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:49.33,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't need.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:54.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.36,0:07:56.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hasumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:12.75,Self tought,,0,0,0,,So, now let's move forward with no fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:15.92,Self tought,,0,0,0,,I'm your ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:20.24,Self tought,,0,0,0,,This is a story of a doctor that saves
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:22.76,Self tought,,0,0,0,,the lost sheep of this modern era.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:32.24,Self tought,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:37.26,Self tought,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the late introduction,\NI'm a psychiatrist, Hino Rintaro
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:47.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:12.78,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Next it's Aizawa Akira-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.78,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:21.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Huh?\NDo you mean that the surgery is gonna be impossible?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.75,0:09:24.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes, surgery is off-label
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:26.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:30.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Prof. Hasumi, what do you mean with\Nthe surgery being off-label?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:33.78,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Until now, you have been performing\Nany sort of risky tumor removal surgeries
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.78,0:09:36.34,Default 1,,0,0,0,,with a successful result, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:38.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Explain your reasons
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:41.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Looking at the MRI image ....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:50.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the tumor in the left temporal lobe\Nhas infiltrated the vicinity of the hippocampus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:55.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It involves a considerable risk to remove the tumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:57.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But there isn't a risk of death, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.52,0:09:59.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There is a risk of damaging the hippocampus with the scalpel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:05.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,One mistake and\Nhe may have a loss of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:12.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You can't refuse this surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:29.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What, what do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.64,0:10:30.85,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Have you also noticed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.08,0:10:40.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Where's Dr. Rintaro?\N{\3c&H573235&}He's examining a patient now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:41.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:44.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Let's talk in my room until he finishes.\N{\3c&H573235&}In your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:48.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If Prof. Hasumi is not able to perform properly,\Nit'll be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.84,0:10:51.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What?\N{\3c&H573235&}I.. I also
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:54.35,Default 1,,0,0,0,,have something I'd like to tell you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:56.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Can I have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:10:59.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,May I?\N{\3c&H573235&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:07.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira-san, do you like to dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:09.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I like to dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:14.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even though I don't remember\Nmuch about the parlor,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:17.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,but I know when I dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:21.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:24.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,When did you start dancing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:28.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Maybe, since I was around 21 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:34.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even since I was little\NI couldn't do anything right,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:39.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,but with dancing, it was the first time\Nmom gave me compliments.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:42.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,"As expected from my daughter", she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:45.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's a memory of your mom that you want to cherish, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.32,0:11:50.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,When I went to the parlor for the first, I was also
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:52.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,impressed with your dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:02.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please come again.\NI'll be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:05.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.\N{\3c&H573235&}Please take care in your way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:20.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino, could you come for a moment?\N{\3c&H573235&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:24.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino, come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:31.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What happened?\N{\3c&H573235&}Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:37.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Confirm the tumor's depths
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:39.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Micro cooper\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:46.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hasumi, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:49.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I knew it, he can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:53.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Also Prof. Hasumi rejected\Na special patient's operation today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:58.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He has succeeded brilliantly operating\Nin similar cases in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:12:59.86,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's not like he can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:03.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,A while ago too, at Dr. Hino's examining room\Nhe stumbled in a strange way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:05.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It didn't seem like a\Nsimple dizziness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.44,0:13:08.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, back then that was what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:14.20,Remembering,,0,0,0,,That wasn't just a mistake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:16.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That was a mistake.\N{\3c&H573235&}It was a mistake, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:18.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,When did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:20.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,At the beginning of this year.\N{\3c&H573235&}This year?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:24.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since the beginning of this year,\Nthe number of his operations has decreased.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:25.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:31.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Dr. Hasumi\Nrefused to take the eyesight test.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:33.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The Prof. doesn't wear glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:37.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In other words, his visual impairment can't be corrected\Nwith glasses
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:40.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The Prof. is a brain surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:43.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If there's a problem in the brain,\Nhe should be able to deal with it on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:45.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:47.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,A visual impairment that can't be corrected with glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:50.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It might be a psychogenic visual impairment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:13:58.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:05.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:09.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Have you decided to schedule the surgery yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:13.33,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's under consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:16.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There are the risks I mentioned this morning\Nand more..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.23,0:14:18.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It looks like you don't understand this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:20.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.72,0:14:26.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If we can solve this time's case\Nwith Kusunoki Minister,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:29.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the talk about the new Hospital\Nwill go smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.23,0:14:31.27,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You'll become a lifesaver
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:34.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,hard to replace, for both parent and son.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:36.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If that happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.22,0:14:40.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,nobody will complain when you become\Nthe new hospital's director.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.72,0:14:42.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Huh..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:46.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You said it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:49.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,"I want to help,\Nno matter whether it's one or many patients,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:53.29,Default 1,,0,0,0,,at the finally established cutting-edge\NToshiminami International Medical Center."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.29,0:14:56.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This dream will come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:58.71,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:15:01.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What are you hesitating about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:03.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You don't have the right to say 'no'
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.73,0:15:06.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do not say he may\Nlose his memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:09.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm the one that saved you\Nfrom medical lawsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:11.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do not forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:17.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Until tomorrow,\Nwithout exceptions, start scheduling the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:19.71,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:21.71,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:25.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mom,\NI'm going to the lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.72,0:15:28.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Have a nice day. Be careful on your way there.\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:32.78,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, sis, welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:35.31,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah mother,\NI'm sorry, I'll get ready really fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.31,0:15:37.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's okay, if you're tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:41.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why don't you take a day off?\NFrom the lessons and also the parlor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.74,0:15:44.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, but..\N{\3c&H573235&}It's fine, once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.22,0:15:52.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry,\NI'm always causing you inconveniences.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.25,0:15:54.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, I also
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.82,0:16:00.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, until now\NI didn't realize anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:06.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You know, the Akira in you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:09.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and the Yumeno in you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:12.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I like both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:13.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:23.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mother...\N{\3c&H573235&}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:33.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:42.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:48.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:52.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:55.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Isn't that strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.52,0:16:58.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even you, mother,\Nhave been brainwashed by Hino-rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:04.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mother, if I leave the parlor,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:07.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it'll be bad for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:10.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,who's earning with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.23,0:17:14.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno..?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:28.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If it's psychogenic,\NI wonder what's the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:31.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The director is going to do a new hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:32.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You knew it, right?\N{\3c&H573235&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:36.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The rumor is about who will be the\Nnew director there? Dr. Hasumi
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.44,0:17:39.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh_ Who gave that information?\N{\3c&H573235&}Nurse station.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:42.81,Default 1,,0,0,0,,They are well informed.\N{\3c&H573235&}That's scary in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.81,0:17:48.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, I wonder if the friction of such hospital politics\Naren't accumulating.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:51.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If he is that much cornered\Nisn't it better to refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:55.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,They have different sense of values than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:56.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even though we're all doctors?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:18:00.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,To say that is really foolish, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:04.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Those people in order to climb the stairs\Nof the White Tower University Hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:07.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and because of that they are sacrificing a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:10.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sacrificing..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:14.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there's a need to pay such a price\Nin order to climb.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:16.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is it not the same for you, Rintaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:17.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:23.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because you, aren't you doing this for you mom\Neven at the expense of yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:28.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's the same for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.72,0:18:32.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Fighting and doing their best for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.21,0:18:40.71,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry..\Nfor suddenly starting to say weird things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.30,0:18:48.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mizushima, I have something to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:49.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:58.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hasumi. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.23,0:19:00.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:05.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Professor, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:07.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:13.31,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino wants to have a talk with you.\N{\3c&H573235&}Hino? But we have a meeting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.31,0:19:16.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since we can contact with the brain surgery department, do not worry.\N{\3c&H573235&}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:18.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You will excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.74,0:19:20.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:23.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What's going on! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:26.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:42.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:54.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry, Dr. Hasumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.24,0:19:56.77,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.77,0:19:59.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're known for pushing things this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.73,0:20:03.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I can't adjust\Nin a good way to your approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:05.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It seems you have a problem with your vision?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:09.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What can you do about it?\N{\3c&H573235&}I can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.24,0:20:11.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So it does not solve anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:14.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,A clue for a solution might be grasped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:20.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Your face is blurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:25.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I can' read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:29.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I've constriction of the visual field. The acuity is 0.01.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:34.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The cephalic MRI found no abnormalities.\NNo abnormalities in the optic nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.23,0:20:36.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The cause is unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:39.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I do not see any solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:41.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hasumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:44.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Will you receive my examination?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:46.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You want to say it's psychogenic visual impairment?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.56,0:20:50.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't know that yet.\N{\3c&H573235&}I dislike your field.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.73,0:20:53.71,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr., I'm also a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:56.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I understand those current painful feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:20:59.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't care if you're willing to feel sympathy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:03.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,At this point there's nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.73,0:21:09.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hello.\N{\3c&H573235&}Ah, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.23,0:21:11.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking about calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.72,0:21:14.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is it about the Minister's son, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.36,0:21:16.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Of course it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:20.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The Minister is waiting for reply as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:22.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What are you hesitating about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:25.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Or is it that you want to miss this opportunity?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.32,0:21:26.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.36,0:21:29.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I've already invested hundreds of millions on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.76,0:21:32.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, do not put me to shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:34.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.71,0:21:42.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even without that,\Nmy stomach constantly hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:50.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah.. I want to drink tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:54.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino's tea..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.73,0:21:57.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:21:59.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Minister Ike is angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.22,0:22:21.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I won't accept any other answer but a 'Yes'!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.72,0:22:27.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Give an answer Hasumi! An answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.26,0:22:29.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm your lifesaver, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.24,0:22:37.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.22,0:22:39.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.73,0:22:47.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh? Hasumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.32,0:22:52.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I really hate that guy.\NThat's all. The end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.40,0:22:55.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Senpai, let's reduce this a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.96,0:22:58.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why are you talking like a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.24,0:23:01.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please hear what I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.73,0:23:05.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.25,0:23:07.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, even we used to be contemporaries,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.22,0:23:09.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it's been already 10 years since\NI quit that Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.24,0:23:12.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hasumi suffers a visual impairment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.23,0:23:20.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Certainly, that was odd. 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.32,0:23:23.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Something must have happened in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.74,0:23:27.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll make some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.74,0:23:33.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.73,0:23:40.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You ran out of tea again, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.73,0:23:42.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.92,0:23:48.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,A medical malpractice"?\N{\3c&H573235&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.24,0:23:52.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She was also an Ennoji's special patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.76,0:23:56.33,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1\u0}"The victim is Satonaka Mizuki-san, 31-year-old,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.33,0:24:00.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}daughter of a certain famous confectionery maker's director.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.24,0:24:02.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.56,0:24:04.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She was also my patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.74,0:24:05.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.72,0:24:08.64,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Everyone\Nspeaks bad things about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.48,0:24:11.44,Remembering,,0,0,0,,I'm being observed, all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.16,0:24:12.84,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Even now..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.60,0:24:16.29,Remembering,,0,0,0,,No ... Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.64,0:24:19.22,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Satonaka-san
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.16,0:24:21.24,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Let's calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.74,0:24:24.92,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Satonaka-san, let's calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.44,0:24:27.75,Remembering,,0,0,0,,It's okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.75,0:24:30.27,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Let's calm down, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.27,0:24:31.84,Remembering,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.74,0:24:36.74,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Let's take a deep breath, slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.74,0:24:38.40,Remembering,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.44,0:24:39.72,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Yes, exhale.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.96,0:24:42.75,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Yes, like that.\NOkay, one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.75,0:24:43.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.92,0:24:46.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Paranoia and short-term memory disorder
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.20,0:24:48.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}were observed at Satonaka-san's first medical
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.36,0:24:52.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}examination, and she\Nwas suspected to suffer from schizophrenia."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.60,0:24:55.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.40,0:25:01.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"But, her attending physician, Mr. Araki,\Nfrom symptoms such as seizures,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.23,0:25:04.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}after carrying out a re-examination,\Ndiagnosed a temporal lobe epilepsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.22,0:25:09.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even, Mr. Hasumi, a brain surgeon from the same hospital,\Ndetermined the same diagnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.80,0:25:12.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And Satonaka-san's diagnosis was confirmed."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.40,0:25:14.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.96,0:25:18.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even at that time, he..
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.73,0:25:21.84,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.74,0:25:25.74,Remembering,,0,0,0,,That surgical procedure,\Nwill left a memory disorder, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.74,0:25:28.26,Remembering,,0,0,0,,But, in this case\Nthe high stability of
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.26,0:25:31.33,Remembering,,0,0,0,,the selective amygdalohippocampectomy, is the best alternative.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.33,0:25:34.92,Remembering,,0,0,0,,If so, the outside of the brain tissue\Nalmost won't require a resection.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.73,0:25:37.48,Remembering,,0,0,0,,What are you nervous about?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.00,0:25:39.28,Remembering,,0,0,0,,With your skills
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.56,0:25:43.76,Remembering,,0,0,0,,you can preserve the hippocampus with the latest\Nmultiple subpial transections surgery,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.92,0:25:45.80,Remembering,,0,0,0,,and you can also preserve the memories, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.52,0:25:48.08,Remembering,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Hasumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.16,0:25:51.31,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Please.\N{\3c&H555557&}I refuse
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.74,0:25:58.04,Remembering,,0,0,0,,You, since when\Nyou've become that self-protective 
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.74,0:26:02.74,Remembering,,0,0,0,,The latest surgery procedure that you mention, \Nhasn't yet been settled in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.04,0:26:07.23,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.52,0:26:10.04,Remembering,,0,0,0,,The memories..
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.64,0:26:15.72,Remembering,,0,0,0,,are the equivalent of life for a patient!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.23,0:26:20.88,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.96,0:26:25.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"It resulted in the Hospital accepting Mr. Hasumi's opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.80,0:26:30.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although surgery was successful,\NSatonaka-san developed the feared sequela,  
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.00,0:26:33.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}she lost her memory."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.36,0:26:36.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's enough already about that talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.36,0:26:40.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Take that and leave,\NI'm feeling bad, move.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.23,0:26:42.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.72,0:26:50.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The cause of this, was seen as a medical error\Nfor the patient and her family,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.22,0:26:54.81,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and they urged the Hospital\Nand sued both doctors, Araki and Hasumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.81,0:26:58.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, 2 months later, both sides\Nunexpectedly settled on an indefinite figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.75,0:27:02.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What happened behind that settlement\Nis unknown."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.22,0:27:05.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.22,0:27:07.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Senpai, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.74,0:27:10.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.56,0:27:12.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I told you to leave, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.75,0:27:15.82,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dir. Ennoji was involved with the settlement, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.82,0:27:17.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.73,0:27:21.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Satonaka-san, after that..\N{\3c&H573235&}Ask it to Hasumi
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.24,0:27:24.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.22,0:27:37.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.44,0:27:43.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Oh ... you fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.73,0:27:47.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.27,0:27:56.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1\u0\b0}Mother, thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.74,0:27:59.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1\u0}Yumeno, thank you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.73,0:28:03.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1\u0}But do not come out anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.73,0:28:26.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ruriko,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.72,0:28:32.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.24,0:28:37.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Jun-chan, just\Ncan you go and buy cigarettes?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.75,0:28:43.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.24,0:28:46.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,How much do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.24,0:28:49.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Huh? what? Is that kind of talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.24,0:28:51.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I really like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.73,0:28:54.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The money,\NI'll get it somehow,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.76,0:28:57.82,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please, just don't meet Yumeno again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.82,0:28:59.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.36,0:29:03.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Oh isn't that interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.80,0:29:08.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah\NI want 100 million,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.08,0:29:10.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it in 50 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.88,0:29:13.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I came up with a nice idea, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.25,0:29:17.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I will certainly prepare for you the 50 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.32,0:29:20.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, about Yumeno..
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.22,0:29:23.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Promise not to meet Yumeno anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.23,0:29:25.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,On this street.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.25,0:29:28.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh!? \N You're really giving me the 50 million?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.72,0:29:30.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.73,0:29:34.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you're giving me the 50 million? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.32,0:29:38.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.73,0:29:42.21,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.21,0:29:45.21,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.21,0:29:48.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.22,0:29:52.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.48,0:29:56.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I am sorry to have asked you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.04,0:30:06.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.72,0:30:09.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I heard from Akari senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.32,0:30:14.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the fact about the medical accident, 10 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.75,0:30:17.92,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Satonak-san developed the feared sequela
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.20,0:30:20.36,Remembering,,0,0,0,,she lost her memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.24,0:30:25.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Also about she's dead?\N{\3c&H573235&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.88,0:30:28.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That patient died six months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.83,0:30:34.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.25,0:30:36.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Somehow I couldn't just leave it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.60,0:30:39.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I went to the funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.68,0:30:51.48,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Why did you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.12,0:30:54.08,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.92,0:30:58.96,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Why did you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.40,0:31:03.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,All I could do was to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.40,0:31:05.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,During 10 years..
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.12,0:31:10.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since the operation\NSatonaka-san lived for 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.88,0:31:12.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I did not expect that outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.72,0:31:15.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, her mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.40,0:31:19.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,every single day, had to listened from her own daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.44,0:31:23.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,"Are you really my mother?"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.75,0:31:26.72,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Are you really my mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.04,0:31:29.29,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She continued to ask that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.60,0:31:35.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The day of the funeral,\Nshe faced to me and said,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.23,0:31:37.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It'd have been better..
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.08,0:31:39.84,Remembering,,0,0,0,,It'd have been better..
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.73,0:31:43.04,Remembering,,0,0,0,,if my daughter and I
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.76,0:31:45.04,Remembering,,0,0,0,,ten years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.77,0:31:53.27,Remembering,,0,0,0,,if you had killed both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.44,0:31:58.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,"Memories are the equivalent to life for the patient"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.48,0:32:03.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The words that Araki told me at that time\Nwere true.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.72,0:32:06.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What is important as a doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.12,0:32:14.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,is not just to keep them alive,\Nbut to save that person's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.96,0:32:24.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,From the moment I become aware\Nof the meaning of those words
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.24,0:32:28.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,my vision began to decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.73,0:32:30.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hansumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.64,0:32:36.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The more you try to\Nforget and deny the feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.81,0:32:39.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,all the more stronger that feeling will grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.60,0:32:42.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,To break this vicious circle,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.25,0:32:46.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,first, you have to accept that memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.84,0:32:51.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you may not be able to really\Nforget that memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.92,0:32:58.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,For me,\Nthere's also an unforgettable memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.48,0:33:01.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I haven't overcome that memory yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.12,0:33:03.44,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Rintaro
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.24,0:33:10.74,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Mom, you try your best too.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.04,0:33:18.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,However, I
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.44,0:33:20.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I've learned from a lot of patients,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.44,0:33:24.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Those patients visiting the doctor's office,\Neveryone,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.74,0:33:28.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,has to face a painful memory that is piercing their hearts,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.88,0:33:30.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and to reach to an agreement somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.44,0:33:34.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That has become my support.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.80,0:33:39.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,For Dr. Hasumi too,\Nfrom now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.84,0:33:45.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I think that you should slowly start to accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.48,0:33:49.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.04,0:33:52.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You have already started to accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.80,0:33:56.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's why,\Na sign appeared on your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.28,0:34:01.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you were me, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.24,0:34:04.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,More than the fact that I can't see by now
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.92,0:34:07.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I no longer worth as a surgeon anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.23,0:34:10.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I would
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.96,0:34:15.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,slowly take a rest in order to heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.32,0:34:20.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.73,0:34:23.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What are you doing in here, Hasumi-kun?\N{\3c&H573235&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.73,0:34:26.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The condition of the Minister's son suddenly changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.25,0:34:29.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He's arriving soon,\Nmove quickly towards the operation room.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.72,0:34:31.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ha.. \N{\3c&H573235&}Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.74,0:34:33.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No matter what, the operation must be successful!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.74,0:34:36.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Director, please wait.\N{\3c&H573235&}This isn't your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.26,0:34:38.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hasumi-kun, just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.23,0:34:42.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.25,0:34:49.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr., you should know!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.22,0:34:51.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What would happen now,\Nif you operate with that body.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.74,0:34:53.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm a doctor\NI can't afford doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.73,0:34:54.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hasumi
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.48,0:34:58.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What about the patient?\N{\3c&H573235&}He just entered the operation room, please hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.00,0:35:02.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Let's look for another hospital.\N{\3c&H573235&}We won't make it on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.96,0:35:07.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mitsushima-kun, help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.74,0:35:09.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.22,0:35:24.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He was in a state of confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.24,0:35:27.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,An enlargement of the lateral ventricle is observed in the CT.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.74,0:35:30.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What do you think?\N{\3c&H573235&}I think it's an obstructive hydrocephalus.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.75,0:35:32.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I've the same opinion, the vitals?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.25,0:35:35.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Blood pressure 100,\Nthe heart rate has improved to 80.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.25,0:35:36.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.75,0:35:39.81,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'd do a craniotomy, performing a tumor removal.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.81,0:35:44.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The sub-temporal\Nor the inferior corner approach ..
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.24,0:35:46.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There are chances of leaving the hippocampus?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.24,0:35:56.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I think there're possibilities of cutting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.72,0:35:58.77,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Everybody, without resting a hand, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.77,0:36:01.83,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I can't operate today.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.83,0:36:06.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In fact, this last half a year\Nmy eyesight has continued to deteriorate.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.75,0:36:10.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mizushima-kun will be the surgeon instead.\NIt should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.24,0:36:12.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll give all the instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.24,0:36:15.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Secure firmly the surgical field,\Nthe base of the temporal,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.24,0:36:18.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,so as not to damage the choroidal artery.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.24,0:36:19.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hurry up.\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.76,0:36:52.31,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry, about the surgery..
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.31,0:36:54.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Mizushima will be the surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.23,0:36:56.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mizushima will?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.73,0:37:10.78,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yumeno's memories are also my memories
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.78,0:37:13.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.73,0:37:16.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So it's okay if you don't come out anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.27,0:37:36.77,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.23,0:37:40.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira-san
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.73,0:37:42.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.23,0:37:46.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Come out a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.22,0:37:49.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.23,0:38:15.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.52,0:38:16.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, how many hours will it take?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.92,0:38:19.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to show on the monitor\Nhow is the surgery?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.64,0:38:23.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, it's okay.\NMy blood is weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.22,0:38:38.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The fusiform gyrus is in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.22,0:38:40.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Slide a little the brain spatula.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.04,0:38:44.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Expand the base of the temporal.\N{\3c&H573235&}Understood
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.40,0:38:50.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Fixation off.\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.23,0:38:53.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,On.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.25,0:38:56.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Bipolar.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.74,0:39:18.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumechiyo will give me\N50 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.74,0:39:22.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mother will give you?\N{\3c&H573235&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.73,0:39:27.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's why I don't longer need you to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.52,0:39:31.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Take care, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.32,0:39:34.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Byyy~e!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.23,0:39:43.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.75,0:39:45.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.72,0:39:48.28,Remembering,,0,0,0,,When are you coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.64,0:39:51.29,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.32,0:39:59.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.40,0:40:02.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.80,0:40:05.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What does it mean that you don't need me?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.22,0:40:06.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,please ....
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.76,0:40:09.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.28,0:40:12.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do not leave me! I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.48,0:40:16.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mom..
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.25,0:40:21.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, I forgot, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.36,0:40:23.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here, I forgot\NI brought your candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.92,0:40:24.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.24,0:40:29.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here\N{\3c&H573235&}No..
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.73,0:40:32.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't want it, don't want..\N{\3c&H573235&}Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.84,0:40:35.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't need you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.00,0:40:39.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't need you..
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.72,0:40:42.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.25,0:40:55.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.31,0:41:00.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.23,0:41:02.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.24,0:41:12.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.88,0:41:18.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino,\Na phone call from Yumeno-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.80,0:41:22.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please hurry, she's quite upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.56,0:41:25.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.32,0:41:32.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hello, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.23,0:41:36.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr., you said it, right, doctor..
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.80,0:41:39.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Did something happen? Akira-san
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.44,0:41:45.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,My mother's memories\Nalso Yumeno's memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.16,0:41:46.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you said that I should cherish them..
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.04,0:41:50.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, my mother is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.20,0:41:53.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why..?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.77,0:41:59.27,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why..
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.00,0:42:03.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I no longer need you, she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.44,0:42:07.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira-san, where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.24,0:42:16.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.84,0:42:23.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,We have complete exposure of the\Nhippocampus and amygdala
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.84,0:42:24.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,How does it look?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.40,0:42:32.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There's a severe adhesion of the tumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.74,0:43:00.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.23,0:43:02.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Micro Cooper.\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.96,0:43:06.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Make sure not to hurt the hippocampus.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.22,0:43:08.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.40,0:43:09.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.68,0:43:11.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is Akira-san there?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.04,0:43:15.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She went out, but\Ndid something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.80,0:43:18.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yuriko-san\Nseems to have said to Akira-san
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.25,0:43:21.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,that she doesn't need her anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.44,0:43:22.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.36,0:43:25.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Actually, I ....
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.36,0:43:28.96,Remembering,,0,0,0,,The money,\NI'll get it somehow,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.48,0:43:32.12,Remembering,,0,0,0,,just don't meet Yumeno again.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.23,0:43:33.64,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.04,0:43:37.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is that so.. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.52,0:43:40.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Did I do something I shouldn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.20,0:43:42.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, there is no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.82,0:43:45.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please, if she returns, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.23,0:43:47.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'd like to talk with Akira-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.24,0:43:49.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.73,0:44:03.83,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.56,0:44:05.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.23,0:44:08.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Kusunoki Yūji-sama's surgery\Nhas been successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.44,0:44:10.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Really! That's good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.60,0:44:14.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, contact Minister Ike on the phone.\N{\3c&H573235&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.88,0:44:17.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yea, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.12,0:44:19.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yea, that's good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.78,0:44:29.78,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.28,0:44:37.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.08,0:44:41.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That was a success thanks to Mizushima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.12,0:44:43.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is that so!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.23,0:44:46.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That was truly a great work.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.00,0:44:50.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,By not looking, it's the first time I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.84,0:44:51.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.00,0:44:55.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Memories are stored in the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.25,0:44:58.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's not the brain what we are dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.96,0:45:03.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's memories, it's minds. It's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.04,0:45:08.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The heart of the humans is located in the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.32,0:45:11.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You may not agree with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.84,0:45:14.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, I agree with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.84,0:45:17.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't know the location for the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.76,0:45:20.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And because I don't know,\NI've continued with this work.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.96,0:45:24.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Once again,\NI want to face the patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.73,0:45:26.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is see.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.04,0:45:32.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In order to do that,\Nlet's recover, taking a rest, slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.24,0:45:38.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.24,0:45:40.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.22,0:45:50.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.24,0:46:13.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.20,0:46:33.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.08,0:46:37.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm in need of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.72,0:46:41.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I am in need of money.\N{\3c&H573235&}Please, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.00,0:46:43.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Haven't your mother said\Nthat she doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.88,0:46:47.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,need more money anymore?\N{\3c&H573235&}That's why I need the money, isn't it!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.44,0:46:48.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.92,0:46:51.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because Akira\Nwill be discarded, isn't she!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.04,0:46:53.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,By such a mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.92,0:46:55.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,do you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.20,0:46:59.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira wants to be loved\Nby that mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.88,0:47:02.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's why I need the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.40,0:47:04.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.00,0:47:14.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You\Nwant to erase me away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.24,0:47:19.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira too,\Nshe said she didn't need me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.24,0:47:21.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since you instigate her,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.24,0:47:24.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,to believe she doesn't need me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.68,0:47:36.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I \Nsell flattery to men I don't even like.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.60,0:47:38.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,every night, all types of men..
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.20,0:47:48.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I charm and entertain\Nevery night all kind of men.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.32,0:47:51.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Deceiving, stealing their money..
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.60,0:47:53.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, what is that I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.12,0:47:56.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What is that you understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.12,0:47:59.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why do you want me to disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.23,0:48:06.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.24,0:48:09.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.56,0:48:09.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.20,0:48:14.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I never thought about wanting\Nto erase you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.30,0:48:16.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I just
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.68,0:48:20.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,want to connect both of your times,\NAkira-san and yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.60,0:48:23.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,To have part of your life, part of your time,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.04,0:48:26.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,missing or left out,\Ndoesn't it cause you anxiety?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.92,0:48:31.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san's time\Nand Akira-san's time, both are important.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.44,0:48:37.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Fun memories, painful memories,\Nall of them included are part of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.48,0:48:42.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino-rin, you're really stupid, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.36,0:48:47.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Those memories are really painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.52,0:48:55.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll show you some painful memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.22,0:49:03.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.08,0:49:05.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,A call from the Minister Kusunoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.08,0:49:08.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's Ennoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.72,0:49:09.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, no..!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.76,0:49:12.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's because our neurosurgery team is excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.32,0:49:14.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.68,0:49:16.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah.. thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.16,0:49:19.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,We'll be talking about that matter again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.23,0:49:22.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well, until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.64,0:49:23.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.73,0:49:27.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Good morning.\N{\3c&H573235&}Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.80,0:49:29.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,well, thanks to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.44,0:49:31.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the talk about the new hospital\Nis progressing really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.92,0:49:36.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Your director's office\Nshould be at the top floor facing south? eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.16,0:49:38.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You'll have a view to the courtyard.\N{\3c&H573235&}Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.04,0:49:42.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And, since next time, I'll reserve a seat for\NMinister Kusonoki
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.16,0:49:44.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you should also greet him.\N{\3c&H573235&}About that matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.56,0:49:46.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,in fact,...\N{\3c&H573235&}Dir.! Big problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.88,0:49:49.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,At least knock first, you.\N{\3c&H573235&}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.73,0:49:55.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Have you seen this already?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.75,0:49:57.78,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.78,0:50:11.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.76,0:50:15.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.32,0:50:17.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What's this!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.24,0:50:24.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What's this, \Nwhat's this!!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.16,0:50:26.81,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
